{
	"nodes":[
		{
			"height":80,
			"id":"main_title",
			"styleAttributes":{"border":"invisible","textAlign":"center"},
			"text":"# 🧠 第二大脑操作系统\n**ACCESS + PARA 知识管理架构**",
			"type":"text",
			"width":400,
			"x":400,
			"y":-100
		},
		{
			"height":40,
			"id":"subtitle",
			"styleAttributes":{"border":"invisible","textAlign":"center"},
			"text":"*12k+ 文件 | 2000+ 卡片 | 4000+ 外部资料 | 无限可能*",
			"type":"text",
			"width":400,
			"x":400,
			"y":-20
		},
		{"color":"4","height":900,"id":"access_group","label":"ACCESS 六大支柱","type":"group","width":1400,"x":-100,"y":80},
		{
			"color":"1",
			"height":340,
			"id":"atlas_card",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"left"},
			"text":">[!cc-header] 🗺️ ATLAS\n\n**知识图谱 · 导航中枢**\n\n• [[∑ 全库MOC索引|MOCs]] - 内容地图\n• [[∑ BASE|Bases]] - 数据库视图\n• Canvas - 可视化画布\n• Dataview - 动态查询\n\n---\n*「地图不是领土，但指引方向」*",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":-50,
			"y":130
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":340,
			"id":"calendar_card",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"left"},
			"text":">[!cc-header] 📅 CALENDAR\n\n**时间线 · 生命节奏**\n\n• Daily Notes - 每日记录\n• Weekly Review - 周复盘\n• Monthly Report - 月总结\n• Yearly Vision - 年规划\n\n---\n*「时间是最好的老师」*",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":260,
			"y":130
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":340,
			"id":"cards_card",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"left"},
			"text":">[!cc-header] 🎏 CARDS\n\n**原子笔记 · 思想砖块**\n\n• 一卡一概念\n• 用自己的话重写\n• [[wikilink]] 互联\n• 永久保存价值\n\n---\n*「2000+ 张卡片，每张都是一块乐高」*",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":570,
			"y":130
		},
		{
			"color":"4",
			"height":340,
			"id":"extras_card",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"left"},
			"text":">[!cc-header] ⚙️ EXTRAS\n\n**引擎室 · 自动化**\n\n• Scripts - 维护脚本\n• Templates - 模板系统\n• Prompts - AI 提示词\n• Attachments - 附件资源\n\n---\n*「让重复的事情自动化」*",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":880,
			"y":130
		},
		{
			"color":"5",
			"height":340,
			"id":"sources_card",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"left"},
			"text":">[!cc-header] 📚 SOURCES\n\n**进料口 · 外部输入**\n\n• Articles - 文章笔记\n• Books - 书籍笔记\n• Clippings - 剪藏内容\n• Sync - 自动同步\n\n---\n*「4000+ 条外部资料等待转化」*",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":-50,
			"y":520
		},
		{
			"color":"6",
			"height":340,
			"id":"spaces_card",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"left"},
			"text":">[!cc-header] 🚀 SPACES\n\n**行动区 · PARA 工作区**\n\n• 1-Project - 有截止日期\n• 2-Area - 持续责任\n• 3-Resource - 兴趣主题\n• 4-Archive - 已完成归档\n\n---\n*「按行动属性组织，而非类别」*",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":260,
			"y":520
		},
		{"height":340,"id":"para_detail_group","label":"PARA 详解","type":"group","width":590,"x":570,"y":520},
		{
			"color":"1",
